# DISCUSSION - Community Standards Protocol

DESCRIPTION
  Guidelines for providing feedback on Hive Helsinki community standards

PROCEDURES
  1. FEEDBACK FORMAT
      - State which manual you're discussing
      - Quote specific section
      - Provide clear reasoning for change
      - Suggest specific improvements

  2. QUESTIONS TO CONSIDER
      - Is it clear?
      - Is it relevant?
      - What one thing would you change?

  3. FEEDBACK RECEPTION
      - Document all feedback as close to the target as possible
      - Document all feedback as openly as possible
      - In case of conflict, fix it
      - If you can't fix it, document the conflict

COMMON ERRORS
  - Personal attacks
  - Overwhelming the discussion
  - Lecturing
  - Not asking for help

